THE 1970 GIT REPOSITORY.

THIS REPO CONTAINS COMMITS DATING TO 1970-01-01 000000Z.
EPOCH TIME HAS BEEN APPLIED TO AUTHOR AND COMMITTER FIELDS.

REASON FOR EXISTENCE.
TO OBSERVE BEHAVIOUR OF DATE DISPLAYS.
TO SHOW GIT DATE FIELDS ARE MUTABLE.

HOW TO REPRODUCE.
SET GIT_AUTHOR_DATE AND GIT_COMMITTER_DATE.
EXAMPLE COMMAND FOLLOWS.

GIT_AUTHOR_DATE='1970-01-01T00:00:00 +0000'
GIT_COMMITTER_DATE='1970-01-01T00:00:00 +0000'
GIT COMMIT -M 'TIME TRAVEL ACHIEVED'

CAUTION.
THIS IS EDUCATIONAL ONLY.
FAKING DATES FOR GRAPH MANIPULATION IS DISCOURAGED.

EOF
